# Phase 2 Walkthrough: Investor Identity & Onboarding

I have completed the "Masterpiece" upgrades to the CoreVault AI user profile and onboarding systems. The platform now feels significantly more professional and data-driven.

## Key Accomplishments

### 1. 📂 Enhanced Onboarding Engine
- **Robust Voice Input**: Fixed the "word repetition" issue by implementing a strict `isFinal` result-handling loop for the Web Speech API.
- **Deep Profiling**: Added 3 new steps to capture **Financial Knowledge**, **Investment Horizon**, and **Savings Targets**, enabling the AI Trading Agent to make more personalized suggestions.
- **Improved UX**: Smoother transitions and a 6-step progress indicator.

### 2. 👤 Premium Investor Profile (`SettingsPage`)
- **DP/Avatar Upload**: You can now click on the profile picture to upload a custom image from your PC. It is stored locally as a Base64 string for persistence.
- **"Architect Details" Container**: Added an expandable section that reveals all your detailed onboarding data (Income, Expenses, Knowledge, Life Goals).
- **Fintech Metrics**: Integrated **AI Trust Score** and **Security Level** progress bars to reinforce the secure, AI-driven experience.
- **Fixed "Occupation" Error**: Resolved the TypeScript/Lint error where the occupation field was missing from the user interface.

### 3. 🛡️ Branded QR Identity
- **Branded Design**: The QR code now features the **CoreVault Sparkle Logo** in the center for a premium, verified look.
- **Full Data Payload**: The QR code now contains a comprehensive JSON payload of your entire investor identity (ID, Name, Email, and Onboarding profile).
- **Downloadable ID**: Added a "Download ID Logo" button that generates a PNG file of your QR identity for local storage.

## Verification Results

- **Server Status**: [OK] Running on localhost:3000.
- **Persistence**: [OK] Verified that avatar and onboarding data remain after page refresh.
- **Logic**: [OK] Tested Speech API to ensure no duplicated text.

> [!TIP]
> **Scan to Verify**: You can use your phone camera on the QR code in the "Settings" tab to see the full JSON data structure being sent to the "Wealth Architect."

## Next Steps
We are now ready for **Stage 5: Real-Time Market Fluctuation Engine**, where we will make the dashboard charts truly "come alive" with dynamic logic.
